Items.title: Priam Handmade Leather Passport Cover
Items.description: The Priam Handmade Leather Passport Cover is a great way to protect your passport. It has been designed with the help of our professional designers in order to provide you with an elegant yet practical solution for your travel documents. The design features two compartments that are perfect for storing passports, credit cards, or other small items. This beautiful and long-lasting piece can be used as a card holder or wallet by itself, and it can also double up as a money pouch when not being worn on its own. It can be used as an everyday wallet or you could use it for traveling purposes, such as when going abroad. This handmade high-quality leather passport case will last forever with proper care. The leather passport holder protects your passport from damage while keeping all of its contents secure. Made out of full-grain cowhide crazy horse leather, and it has a nice soft feel. The design of the passport case is simple but elegant, which makes it very suitable for daily use, even as a card wallet. This rustic leather passport holder has been handcrafted by skilled artisans using traditional grain leather manufacturing techniques. Each piece takes features intricate stitching that adds character to each item. This is sure to become one of your travel essentials and a perfect handmade gift idea or a gift for travelers.
